litehtml: litehtml (lightweight HTML rendering engine)
litehtml:
litehtml: litehtml just parses HTML/CSS and places the HTML elements into the
litehtml: correct positions (renders HTML). To draw the HTML elements you have
litehtml: to implement the simple callback interface document_container.
litehtml:
litehtml: This interface is really simple, check it out! The document_container
litehtml: implementation is required to render HTML correctly.
